			<abstract>Saint Lucia, 1981 is a scanned map of the Caribbean country Saint Lucia at a scale of 25,000. The map is comprised with three sheets and georeferenced to the surface of the earth and fit to World Geodetic System (1984) coordinates. The original scanned file with additional information is also provided.</abstract>
